['We wanted to know whether using PNBs compared to no nerve block (no block at all or a placebo nerve block), in people with hip fracture could reduce:
• pain on movement;
• confusion, myocardial infarction, and chest infection;
• death from any cause within six months;
• length of time until people were mobile after surgery; and
• costs of drugs used to manage\xa0pain.']

['We cannot tell from the results whether when compared to Bogota bag, NPWT reduces:
-\xa0the time needed for wounds to completely close;
-\xa0harmful or unwanted effects (bowel perforation);
-\xa0death rate; or
-\xa0length of hospital stay between the groups.']

['We cannot tell from the results whether when compared to an ABThera system, a Suprasorb CNP system reduces:
- the proportion of people with wounds that were successfully closed;
- harmful or unwanted effects (bowel perforation);
- death rate; or
- reoperation rate between the groups.']
